<h1>Problems, puzzles, and games</h1>

<b>David W. Lyons</b><br>
<a href="mailto:lyons@lvc.edu"> lyons@lvc.edu </a>

<p>

This page contains a collection of some of my favorite puzzles and
games.  The level of difficultly varies widely.  Some are accessible
with only high school algebra and geometry background, and others
require some experience in college mathematics courses.

